 popular ideas about gender and language are more complicated than they first appear. This book will change the way you think about language, and give you the tools to challenge the world around you.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aCommunicationxSex differences. 0aSexism in language. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Women's Studies.2bisacsh  a#metoo.  adiscrimination.  afeminism.  afeminist.  agender differences.  agender discrimination.  agender stereotypes.  ahear me, see me.  alanguage and gender.  alanguage and identity.  amansplaining.  amisogyny.  asexism.  avocal fry.  awomen and language.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics and Social Sciences 2018 Englishz978311060401608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311060678240uhttps://doi.org/10.21832/978178309961040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781783099610423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781783099610/original  a978-3-11-060401-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Economics and Social Sciences 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060678-2  MultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018